Terms of Use and Privacy Policy of Diamond Line Abydos
Introduction
This document describes the personal data we collect, how it is used
and shared, as well as the choices you have regarding that data. We
recommend that you read this document, which addresses the main
points of our privacy practices.
Definitions and introductions
Diamond Line Limited Liability Company (hereinafter referred to as
“the Company”): is a company registered in the Commercial Register
under the number 18581 dated 22/11/2018 and its headquarters is
Mazzeh West Villas - Ibn Al Qayem St - Diamond Line Office -
Damascus - Syrian Arab Republic
The company is the operator of the Diamond Line Abydos application
throughout the Syrian Arab Republic.
Diamond Line Abydos Application: It is an electronic application that
connects passengers who wish to use the services available on the
application with the providers of these transport and delivery services
contracted with the company. The application works on iOS and
Android devices and the company is working on updating it to ensure
that the application continues to function

Drivers: Persons who submit contract forms with the company to
carry out transportation or delivery services, or other products and
services available on the application
Overview
a. scope
This document applies to users of the services of the Diamond Line
Abydos application (the “Application”), and this document describes
how Diamond Line LLC (the “Company”) is collected and used. This
notice applies to all users of the application, passengers and Drivers.
This document specifically applies to the following:
This document also controls the collection of other personal data by
the Company, in connection with the services available on the
Application.

III. Data Collection and Use Policies
a. The data we collect
The company combines the following:
Data provided by users to the company, such as information entered
during account creation,
Data generated while using our Services, such as location data, app
usage data, and device data, the following data is collected by the
Company:
Data provided by users. It includes the following:

User profile: We collect data when users create or update accounts

Criminal background check and identity verification: Sometimes we

User-Generated Content: We collect information that Users provide

photographs, or other recordings that users collect.
Data generated while using our services. It includes the following:
Location data: We collect approximate or exact location data from the
user's mobile device, if the user has authorized it. For Drivers, the
company collects this data when the app is running on the front of the
mobile device (when the app is open and visible on the screen). For
passengers, the company collects this data when the app is launched in
the mobile device. Passengers may use the Application without
allowing the Company to collect location data from mobile devices.
However, this may affect some features available in the app. For
example, a user who did not allow the application to collect location

related to the use of our services, including the type of services
requested or provided, order details, delivery information, date and

method. Additionally, if someone uses a promotional code assigned to

Usage data: We collect data about how users interact with our
services. This data includes the dates and times of use,
Communication data: We allow users to communicate with other users
and the Company through the mobile application. For example, we
allow Drivers and passengers to know the mobile number to make
calls if necessary.
Data usage includes the following:
How the company uses data

To enhance the safety of users and the security of our services
To provide customer support
